				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Here's a good method. Store the address of the controller routine at say $40/$41 in ZP. Then when you want to go to the controller routine, do JMP ($40). So if you want to point to a different controller routine, change $40/$41 to the address of the desired routine.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

